	  <Summary>Native .NET integration endpoint -- embed the full OASIS Engine directly in your app, game, or service without needing the REST API.</Summary>
	  <Description>The OASIS Native Integrated EndPoint lets you embed the complete OASIS engine (all managers, providers, HOT-Swappable Provider Architecture) directly into any .NET 10 application, game, or service -- no REST API or separate server required. Ideal for Unity games, desktop apps, and microservices that need direct in-process access to the Avatar/Karma/Holon/Data APIs across 55+ providers. Part of the OASIS Omniverse at https://oasisomniverse.one</Description>
